summary:
- Capital Raising Announcement: ASX plans to undertake a Share Purchase Plan (SPP), and a placement, with participation by ASM’s Chair.  
- Total Capital Raised: Not specified in the document.  
- Key Timetable: SPP opens at 10:00am Perth time on 19 July 2025.  
- Offer Structure: Eligible shareholders can purchase up to $30,000 worth of new fully paid ordinary shares.  
- Disclosure: Offers will be made without disclosure under Part 6D.2 of the Corporations Act; no excluded information or material disclosures required at this time.
